com.iopipe.plugin.trace

Class TraceMeasurement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iopipe.plugin.trace.TraceMeasurement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    public final class TraceMeasurement
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    This class measures a duration of time and is intended to be used with try-with-resources to measure how long a given block of code takes to execute. The measurement may only be closed once.
    Since:
    2018/01/19
